# Windows Defender

This article described the use if Windows Defender and how it put all your security features in one area. If you download third party applications it is shown on Windows defender as well. Windows 10 window defender application
has biometric and facial recognition to make accessing Window defender more secure. Nothing is added to window defender but it does make previous pre-exsisting window security and privacy avaialable to you. Overall it seems to be a great application that shows alot of promise as Windows applications are trying to deter vulnerabiities. 